# WSL-only apt packages.
# Installed by: setup/modules/00-apt-base.sh (profile: wsl)
# Docs:         docs/setup/ubuntu-base.md
#
# Deliberately thin: WSL gets base.list plus these. No GUI packages, no
# systemd-dependent services, no drivers — the Windows host owns all of that.

# Clipboard bridge to the Windows host
wslu
